    "description": "Bunker Builder Simulator：Prologue 只是完整版游戏中等待您的游戏玩法的一部分。<br><br>获取合同，建造、配置并装饰地堡，成为地堡建造专家! 审视你将进行的项目，让你的客户安全有保障、服务很满意！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/e0d34d120c9d84a5e63a3a0f3f906fba.poster.avif?t=1743590313\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/e0d34d120c9d84a5e63a3a0f3f906fba.webm?t=1743590313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/e0d34d120c9d84a5e63a3a0f3f906fba.mp4?t=1743590313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>挖个洞吧！你的大部分合同将在客户的花园中执行。你对材料的选择将是建造地堡的稳固之本，整个地堡项目的耐久度将取决于这一选择。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/73641512210bf23259bc559ebb9dcf59.poster.avif?t=1743590313\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/73641512210bf23259bc559ebb9dcf59.webm?t=1743590313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/73641512210bf23259bc559ebb9dcf59.mp4?t=1743590313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏将提供许多让你有效完成工作的工具。你要亲自切割、焊接、抹灰，而这些只是你任务的一小部分。随着时间的推移你会得到更棒的工具，让你工作更加快速，这就意味着你将拿下更多的合同，更快致富！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/c2e7ecff742cfeefe97a59032278ce95.poster.avif?t=1743590313\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/c2e7ecff742cfeefe97a59032278ce95.webm?t=1743590313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/c2e7ecff742cfeefe97a59032278ce95.mp4?t=1743590313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你将获得大量物品以满足客户的需求。家具、卫生间设施、厨具、桌游等，不胜枚举。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/bf811ef85658d85afc5f478f269bda2a.poster.avif?t=1743590313\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/bf811ef85658d85afc5f478f269bda2a.webm?t=1743590313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148940/extras/bf811ef85658d85afc5f478f269bda2a.mp4?t=1743590313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>建造地堡，确保安全，远离一切危险！",
